name: Pop The Sauce
description:
Always an honor to collaborate with @Brutalisti! Thank you my friend... This piece was inspired by dance, music, and hip-hop culture. Fond memories of break dancing to Herbie Hancock back in the 80's. Boomboxes and cardboard. Enjoy!

Musicians: Andy Sells-drums, Marc Fendel-bass,keyboard, Jimmy James-guitar samples

Recorded & mixed in Seattle, Washington - October 2021
